import React from 'react'
import { List, Grid } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const CheckoutItems = (props) => (
    <List divided inverted relaxed>
      {props.order.map(({name, price, qty}) => (
    <List.Item>
        <List.Content>
          <List.Header>
              {name}
          </List.Header>
          <Grid>
              <Grid.Row>
                  <Grid.Column width={15}>
                  {qty}x
                  </Grid.Column>
                  <Grid.Column width={1}>
                    {price}
                  </Grid.Column>
              </Grid.Row>
          </Grid>
         
        </List.Content>
      </List.Item>
))}
    </List>

)

export default CheckoutItems
